verbose_text: In accordance, the amount of RS in gelatinized starch showed an overall negative correlation with the amylopectin short branch-chain content and with the average chain length of amylopectin when data from starches of the rice cultivar Teqing and its high AAC transgenic line Teqing resistant starch, as well as from normal and high-amylose maize starches, were analyzed [XREF_BIBR].
